---
title: Creamy Double Beef & Veggie Spaghetti Nest with Parmesan Cheese
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! This saucy creation uses a creamy sauce to coat spaghetti, with chunks of tender mince and flavoursome Cheddar. Add veggies that are subtly hidden within the pasta, and you’ve got a new recipe that's sure to please everyone.
